+# Envelope Laws
+
+This directory holds human-readable summaries of the envelope laws that govern
+MFCS–OMEGA. The normative machine-readable modules live under `spec/modules/`.
+
+## Current laws
+
+- `phi-A.md` — Near-recursion attractor law for the φ-governed facet family.
+
+## Source of truth
+
+Use the following repository-local artifacts together:
+
+- `spec/modules/envelope-laws.tla` — compatibility module for generic envelope constraints
+- `spec/modules/EnvelopeLaws.tla` — canonical upper-case module for TLA+ specs
+- `mirror/two_peak_example.json` and `mirror/three_peak_example.json` — compact law-bearing examples
+- `src/lib/oracleKernelCore.ts` — runtime binding of φ-attractor compliance
